OL,3,CFans boo David Beckham and demand
OL,4,Crefund as Messi misses Hong Kong game
OL,6,FInter Miami co-owner David Beckham was
OL,7,Fbooed and angry fans chanted for a
OL,8,Frefund after Lionel Messi did not play
OL,9,Fin a pre-season friendly in Hong Kong.
OL,11,FMessi, who has been suffering with a
OL,12,Fhamstring injury, was left on the
OL,13,Fbench as his side beat a Hong Kong XI
OL,14,F4-1.
OL,16,FIn footage posted on social media,
OL,17,Ffans could be heard chanting "refund"
OL,18,Fbefore a post-match speech from
OL,19,FBeckham was greeted with boos.
