OL,6,FThe Hong Kong government said match
OL,7,Forganisers Tatler Asia could face a
OL,8,Freduction in funding.
OL,10,F"The Government today expressed deep
OL,11,Fdisappointment over Messi not playing
OL,12,Fat Tatler XFEST Hong Kong, Hong Kong
OL,13,FTeam vs Inter Miami CF, and the
OL,14,Forganiser failing to provide a
OL,15,Fdetailed explanation promptly," the
OL,16,Fgovernment said in a statement.
