OL,6,F"The event has been awarded "M" Mark
OL,7,Fstatus, as well as a matching grant of
OL,8,F15 million (Hong Kong dollars; #1.5m)
OL,9,Fand a grant for venue of 1 million by
OL,10,FThe Major Sports Events Committee
OL,11,F(MSEC).
OL,13,F"The Government has also provided a
OL,14,Fvariety of coordination and
OL,15,Fassistance, including venue
OL,16,Farrangement and crowd management, in
OL,17,Forder to offer football fans a
OL,18,Fwonderful game and an opportunity to
OL,19,Fwitness the world-class player
OL,20,Fshowcasing his skills.
