OL,3,CFans boo David Beckham and demand
OL,4,Crefund as Messi misses Hong Kong game
OL,6,F"Many Hong Kong fans looked forward to
OL,7,Fthe match with enthusiasm, and a lot
OL,8,Fof tourists came to Hong Kong
OL,9,Fparticularly for the match.
OL,11,F"The Government, as well as all
OL,12,Ffootball fans, are extremely
OL,13,Fdisappointed that Messi could neither
OL,14,Fplay in the friendly match, nor
OL,15,Fexplain to the fans in person upon
OL,16,Frequest.
