OL,3,CFans boo David Beckham and demand
OL,4,Crefund as Messi misses Hong Kong game
OL,6,F"The way that the organiser and Inter
OL,7,FMiami CF handled the situation could
OL,8,Fnot meet the expectations of the fans
OL,9,Fwho showed strong support to Messi,
OL,10,Fespecially those visitors who came all
OL,11,Fthe way here for the match.
OL,13,F"The Culture, Sports and Tourism
OL,14,FBureau and the MSEC will rely on the
OL,15,Fterms and conditions of the agreement
OL,16,Fin requiring the organiser to take
OL,17,Fresponsibility, including a reduction
OL,18,Fof the amount of funding as a result
OL,19,Fof Messi being not able to play in the
OL,20,Fmatch."
